<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@2.8.2/dist/alpine.min.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-6 py-4 text-left">
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Our Mission</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform duration-200" :class="{ 'rotate-180': open }" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="px-6 pb-4">
          <p>At [Your Company Name], our mission is to provide high-quality, sustainable products that enhance your everyday life. We believe in creating items that reflect our passion for design, quality, and innovation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-6 py-4 text-left">
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Our Values</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform duration-200" :class="{ 'rotate-180': open }" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="px-6 pb-4">
          <p>We are committed to sustainability, ethical sourcing, and giving back to the community. Our values guide every decision we make, from the products we design to the way we interact with our customers and partners.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-6 py-4 text-left">
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Our Story</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform duration-200" :class="{ 'rotate-180': open }" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="px-6 pb-4">
          <p>Founded in [Year], [Your Company Name] started as a small business with a vision to make a difference in the industry. Over the years, we have grown into a global brand while maintaining our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <button @click="open = !open" class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-6 py-4 text-left">
          <span class="text-lg font-semibold">Our Team</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform transition-transform duration-200" :class="{ 'rotate-180': open }" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div x-show="open" class="px-6 pb-4">
          <p>Our team is made up of talented individuals who are passionate about what they do. From designers to customer support, everyone plays a vital role in ensuring we deliver the best products and services to our customers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
